choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for this week.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, or cashews
Sure, here is an example of what you could eat during the day : 
 - Breakfast: 1 cup oatmeal with blueberries and walnuts. 2 cups green tea without sugar;  - Lunch: 3 oz chicken breast + salad (lettuce, tomatoes, cucumber) + hummus dip ; 
- Snack: 1 apple, 1 orange. 
- Dinner : 4 ounces salmon filet cooked in a pan with olive oil and lemon juice. 2 cups brown rice cooked with vegetables such as zucchini or mushrooms;  1 cup green tea without sugar
